						               													<description>Ruddy Vikings is a strategic card game with a cartoon style and a Viking based theme.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;How to play?&amp;#10;The aim of Ruddy Vikings is to destroy the cards in your opponents hand. When you lose all of your cards you lose and are out of the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Ruddy Vikings is super easy to pick up and play and super fun for players of any age with a difficulty curve that starts simple and increases as you learn more strategies. An average game between 2 players lasts approx 5-15 minutes with games of more players lasting longer.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Ruddy Vikings Heroic Deck&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Heroic Deck is filled with all sorts of goodness! Heroic Viking Cards have built in buffers which make them more likely to get past defences. This coupled with new defences and new buffers mean that players never have to stop having fun filled bearded gaming sessions.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Ruddy Vikings is currently live on Kickstarter https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/roundedsquarish/ruddy-vikings-the-beardiest-card-game-ever&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
